        public static org.jfree.chart.ChartPanel generateReceivedPowerGraphForMotes​(Mote mote,
                                                                            int run,
                                                                            Environment environment)
        Generates a received power graph for a specific mote for a specific run, the amount of packets sent and the amount lost. NOTE: this also updates the fields packetsSent and packetsLost to the corresponding values of that mote.
        Parameters:
        mote - The mote to generate the graph of.
        run - The run to generate the graph of
        Returns:
        A Pair containing ChartPanel containing a received power graph and another pair containing 2 integers: the amount of packets sent and the amount lost.
